name: Witch Through Dimensions
description:
Help Witch Girl defeat the evil Dimension Witch and her demon minions in this interdimensional adventure!

made for the GoedWare Game jam #7

controls: 

Move- WASD, Joystick, Dpad(might bug out)

Aim - Mouse, Joystick

Shoot - Mouse Left Click, Right or Left Trigger

game was made with Unity, Krita, Blender 3d and FL studio

additional assets/SFX - gaster blaster SFX belongs to toby fox, pixel art font belongs to Riciery Leal.

was a very fun project to make, hopefully you'll enjoy it too!
